---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Amid the Noise">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="policy-meta">Effective Date: April 2026</p>

    <p>
      Amid the Noise is a personal publication operated by Matthew McClendon.
      This site is designed to share writing, ideas, and research. It does not
      actively collect personal information beyond what is necessary to operate
      and maintain the site.
    </p>

    <h2>Information Collection</h2>
    <p>
      This site does not require user accounts and does not collect personal
      information such as names, addresses, or payment details.
    </p>

    <p>
      If analytics tools are used, they may collect basic, anonymized information such as:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Pages visited</li>
      <li>Time spent on the site</li>
      <li>General location (city or region)</li>
      <li>Device and browser type</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      This information is used solely to understand how the site is used and to
      improve its content and performance.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Basic cookies may be used for analytics or performance purposes. These
      cookies do not identify you personally.
    </p>

    <p>
      You can disable cookies through your browser settings at any time.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>
      This site may contain links to third-party platforms such as LinkedIn,
      Substack, Medium, or GitHub. These sites operate independently and have
      their own privacy policies.
    </p>

    <p>
      Amid the Noise is not responsible for the content or practices of
      third-party websites.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      Because this site does not collect sensitive personal information, data
      risk is minimal. Reasonable measures are taken to ensure the site remains
      secure and stable.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      This policy may be updated as the site evolves. Updates will be reflected
      by revising the effective date above.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For questions regarding this policy, you may contact:
      <br />
      <a href="mailto:info@amidthenoise.com">info@amidthenoise.com</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy-meta {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.2em;
  }
</style>